        <div class="feat-ic" style="background:var(--pink-bg);color:var(--pink)"><i class="fa-solid fa-rotate-left"></i></div>
        <div class="feat-body">
          <span class="feat-num">05</span>
          <h3 itemprop="name">Returns Processing</h3>
          <p itemprop="description">Manage inbound returns with inspection and restocking workflows. Track return reasons and process refunds efficiently.</p>
        </div>
      </li>
      <li class="feat-item" itemprop="itemListElement" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/ListItem">
        <meta itemprop="position" content="6">
        <div class="feat-ic" style="background:var(--cyan-bg);color:var(--cyan)"><i class="fa-solid fa-wand-magic-sparkles"></i></div>
        <div class="feat-body">
          <span class="feat-num">06</span>
          <h3 itemprop="name">Put-Away Rules</h3>
          <p itemprop="description">Auto-suggest bin locations based on product type and velocity. Intelligent slotting to minimize travel time.</p>
        </div>
      </li>
      <li class="feat-item" itemprop="itemListElement" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/ListItem">
        <meta itemprop="position" content="7">
        <div class="feat-ic" style="background:var(--blue-bg);color:var(--blue)"><i class="fa-solid fa-layer-group"></i></div>
        <div class="feat-body">
          <span class="feat-num">07</span>
          <h3 itemprop="name">Wave Planning</h3>
          <p itemprop="description">Group orders into waves for efficient batch picking. Optimize pick paths and reduce warehouse travel time.</p>
        </div>
      </li>
      <li class="feat-item" itemprop="itemListElement" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/ListItem">
        <meta itemprop="position" content="8">
        <div class="feat-ic" style="background:var(--purple-bg);color:var(--purple)"><i class="fa-solid fa-bullseye"></i></div>
